Departures - Season 1 (2008) [BrRip MKV]

Aimed at the adventure seeker, Gemini Award winning series departures follows friends Scott and Justin as they leave their lives behind in search of unique experiences and adventures abroad. An original Canadian production created by Andre Dupuis and Scott Wilson and produced by Jessie Wallace and Steven Bray.
